# 64-byte Ed25519 secret key. Accepts:
#   - base58 string (matches InFlow SolanaClient.Account.getSeed() and Phantom export)
#   - JSON byte array of 64 ints in 0..255 (matches solana-keygen's output file)
SOLANA_PRIVATE_KEY=
TARGET_URL=http://localhost:3000/api/widgets

# Optional: SPL Token mint to pay in. Defaults to Circle's canonical
# devnet USDC (`4zMMC9srt5Ri5X14GAgXhaHii3GnPAEERYPJgZJDncDU`). Override
# when paying a sandbox or seller that uses a custom test mint — the
# buyer's `accepts[]` policy filter will drop any non-matching mint, so
# this value must equal the seller's advertised `asset` for the
# settlement to proceed. The KEEP/drop policy log on each 402 prints
# every offered mint so you can pick the right one.
# SOLANA_PAYMENT_MINT=
